      • conservativeEstimateRatio

        public final double conservativeEstimateRatio
        The amount of times you want to substract the standard deviation from the mean to get the TrueSkill estimate. In normal TrueSkill the mean would be 25, the standard deviation would be 25/3 and this ratio would be 3. The TrueSkill estimate would then be lower than the actual skill in 99% of the cases.
